{"tid":424409,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"講野夾個“for”字做咩鳩","createTime":"2017-10-04T16:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T09:24:30.000Z","uid":62487,"like":35,"dislike":622,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"8bd6fa26dc8d3406f890744038ede186db58bc63","tid":424409,"uid":62487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:12:40.000Z","msg":"依家好似咩人講野就會用&ldquo;for&rdquo;黎代替 用於/用作/用黎/愛黎。<br />\n<br />\n依個用法真係好奇怪，講緊廣東話，無啦啦夾個英文介詞做乜鳩姐？又唔係d咩特別嘅地方名，人名，個腦無辦法用廣東話諗野咩？<br />\n<br />\n再唔係，單字一個 比 都得呀，依家唔係無單音喎，用for 專業d？順口d？<br />\n<br />\n每次聽到人地咁講，第一時間覺得燥，下一秒就心諗條友係咪真係咁撚蠢，係要夾個英文字先識講野。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n「等我屌醒你地」 香港係for 搵錢，唔係for 生活<br />\n<br />\n發明冷氣條友唔係for你地用黎開25.5度呀戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n學歷只係for你升職用，你讀撚完工程落到site傻下傻下咁識撚做咩\t<br />\n<br />\n移民啦，香港真係唔適合居住，只係for你搵夠就走點解係自己既地方比人入侵係要自己走而唔係趕走入侵者點趕?"},{"pid":"de086557326d88a0c6f0a899d6431017ccc6ea36","tid":424409,"uid":79287,"like":555,"dislike":7,"score":548,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:15:43.000Z","msg":"你自己都用site啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c99af7cb06a1a7999b7842b4c04a158e92ed2e7","tid":424409,"uid":32810,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:16:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你自己都用site啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f4a28877ce4e1a4c4dec1054c882268adda6a4","tid":424409,"uid":79266,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:17:54.000Z","msg":"真係冇第樣嘢屌咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32154a7b84b99653eeb0f45b2a30d962697427d","tid":424409,"uid":76098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:18:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你自己都用site啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br /